  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Molo's Revenge is an incremental game where you help Molo take revenge against George the mountain giant, who has destroyed Molo's village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dig</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Molo is a mole dragon who loves to dig. And what better way to take revenge against a mountain by digging!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather and Upgrade</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring the resources from destroying blocks back to base camp and buy powerful upgrades to help you dig better!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Friends Together Strong</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find unique and powerful allies to help with your endeavour and make the mountain giant pay!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Molo's Revenge is an incremental game where you help Molo take revenge against George the mountain giant, who has destroyed Molo's village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dig</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Molo is a mole dragon who loves to dig. And what better way to take revenge against a mountain by digging!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather and Upgrade</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring the resources from destroying blocks back to base camp and buy powerful upgrades to help you dig better!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Friends Together Strong</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find unique and powerful allies to help with your endeavour and make the mountain giant pay!</p>",
